UPDATE [dbo].[NEW_QUESTION] SET [Simple_Question]='Does the organization define the levels of independence for testers as:• None – no independence required. Developer can perform the testing. • Independent person – the person who performs the testing cannot be one of the developers of the product. • Independent department – the person who performs the testing cannot report to the same first line manager as any developers of the product. Alternatively, they could be a member of a quality assurance (QA) department. • Independent organization – the person who performs the testing cannot be part of the same organization as any developers of the product. An organization can be a separate legal entity, a division of a company or a department of a company that reports to a different executive such as a vice president or similar level?' WHERE [Question_Id] = 16479
